==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Jackstone
<hw>Jack"stone`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One of
the pebbles or pieces used in the game of jackstones.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> (<pluf>pl.</pluf>) <def>A game played with five small
stones or pieces of metal. See 6th <er>Chuck</er>. Also called
<altname>jacks</altname>. See <er>jack</er>{12}, <pos>n.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Jackstraw</ent>⟦br⟧
